Elgeyo Marakwet governor has stopped ward reps from allocating Sh100 million to construct the governor and speaker’s mansions in the 2018-19 budget. Governor Alex Tolgos on Friday said he told the MCAs to shoot down the proposal ahead of the budget reading on Thursday.“I told the MCAs that I will not assent to the appropriation if the Sh100 million for mansions is included because this is not our priority,” he said.The county assembly passed a Sh5 billion budget for 2018-19. Click here for
the latest political news